summary: This mod adds a Dr Manhattan to your game.
descriptionHtml:
You should be able to find him at the Winking Skeever. Unfortuantely sometimes he doesn\'t like to show up there. If you do not see him just open up the console and type \"help Manhattan\"

Followed by player.placeatme(his number) 1

And yes there are no pictures because.. well.. It would spoil the fun if you saw him here first! And yes... He is naked.
author: AlphaQ23
